- `dox cat goreleaser docs/install.md --no-line-numbers` shows raw content
- `dox cat goreleaser docs/install.md --offset 10 --limit 5` shows 5 lines from line 10
- `dox cat goreleaser docs/install.md --json` shows structured JSON

